### Programmatic API

{{pkg.name}} provides programmatic API which enables you to execute {{pkg.name}} commands from Node.js program.

```javascript
var fur = require('fur');
fur.banner('my-banner.svg', {
    "text": "coz",
    "color": "o",
    "font": "aa",
    "style": "plain",
    "format": "svg"
}, function (err) {
});
```